data.message:
CI: Introduce Advanced CI and CD

This commit introduces new advanced CI with multiple stages viz.
 - Caching: Caches the build
 - Building
 - Basic Testing: TO-DO for future with proper unit testing
 - Deploy: Deploys the website where during MR we can deploy and test with each
MR having different deployment and purging it when the review is good.
 - Pages: Deploy to GitLab pages at the end.

We are using surge.sh service for CD.
Thanks to @monden for his CI Works for Gatsby Blog with which we have made this.
